All Classes

Class Description
Address
This is the superclass to all of the classes concerning the address, containing the toString and equals methods which are later overridden in the child classes.
CivicAddress
Civic address class contains all of the attributes and methods concerning the civic address of the clinics for the vaccination facilities.
CivicAddress.province
enum which holds the abbreviations of the provinces.
domainAddress
This class is used to store and handle the attributes and methods concerning the domain address/website of the clinics.
Driver
The driver class is where all of the classes and methods created in the classes are used
EmailAddress
This class handles the methods and attributes concerning the email address of the clinic and those of the patients getting vaccinated.
Patient
The Patient class handles and stores methods concerning the patient's information and their vaccination statuses.
TelecomAddress
This class stores and handles attributes and methods concerning the phone number of the patient and clinics.
Vaccine
Vaccine class contains the attributes and methods concerning the vaccine and when/where it is taken.
Vaccine.vaxType
enum holding type vaccine the patient receives.
WebPageAddress
This class stores and handles methods concerning the webpage addresses of the clinics.
